{"tid":1508160,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM唔好再玩分化","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T13:04:51.000Z","uid":222817,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f402e378961dd29c6bdf6984ae089e2133199fad","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"試下體諒下前線、真勇武做嘅行為。<br />\n佢哋嘅諗法同行為，甚至覺悟都行得比我哋前。<br />\n係咪想事後又好似雨傘、魚蛋之後後悔，<strong></strong>內疚都唔住班義士？<br />\n連登其實都好一言堂 ，意見一唔主流就話係鬼。<br />\n講一句說話好容易，但係可唔可以諗埋可以帶嚟嘅後果？<br />\n每一個comment積少成多好容易帶錯風向就令越嚟越多人跟錯。<br />\n佢哋付嘅代價比我哋都大，我哋又有咩資格同佢哋割蓆？<br />\n佢哋承受嘅壓力已經好多，請唔好要佢哋承受嚟自我哋嘅壓力 ，好嘛？<br />\n請記住 不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油 香港加油<br />\n（利申：企得前嘅和理非）<br />\nSorry for 1999 不喜請插"},{"pid":"115c5fe0df221941af316916c9c245c77b498961","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9350c796f18e3d44e10dd7dc9f25e85741fd09bf","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:43.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"d6b879ad0b533cb33c2b12c0c02bf1607bc40193","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a5f9587198e925219cbe24daf241bf9a46db3173","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:24:03.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"09634217c08aa5af9d3c347863c50b0b5460f227","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:24:13.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6925dcc1a3376c09d48ab9bca44c86ce073cc7b2","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:24:23.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"acbd0bd9ec3d4aa82a48b1f28168f47eeb7a5d05","tid":1508160,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"236276863da438515cdd691aaa4494dabefcded3","tid":1508160,"u